Visualisations¶

In visualiation 1, this is intended to produce a relationship between retweet count and favorite count of each tweet and attain a correlation between the two variables.

It was therefore noticed that there is a positive correlation between the two variables implying that as a tweet attains more retweets, it attains the favorite selection and if a tweet attains less retweets, it attains low favorite selection as well.

In visualition 2, a broad study and analysis is made on the different numeric variables and a seaborn pairplot is made to attain a relationship study and pattern discovery in the numeric data.
